// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3951 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9aa17695-905f-576c-ad19-68704993d72d

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
